            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Some consider the '57 Chevy to be the best American car of all time. Looking resplendent in red, white, and chrome, this '57 is an excellent example of the breed.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "heading",
